(8, 9, 'Software Testing Engineer', 'Testing Engineer', '20000', '25000', 'Experienced', '0', '1', ' Sector-63 Noida, Uttar Pradesh, India', 'CSS, JQuery, HTML, Javascript, PHP, Software Testing, Test Engineering, SQL Database, Test Scripts Test Cases, Tracking project related Issue logs, SQL database, test methodologies.', '<p>Should have experience in creating Test Plans, Test scripts, Test cases. Should have around 1 year of experience in manual testing. Should have experience in web and mobile apps testing. Proper knowledge of different test methodologies and attention to details. Demonstrated skills in understanding the product from code level to production. Should have good experience in SQL database. Skills Required - PreferredGood knowledge of HTML and CSS and basics in PHP is a plus. Debugging at source code level would be a massive plus. Strong skills in JavaScript, jQuery would be a massive plus. Should demonstrate the ability to think out of the box. Responsibilities Testing all aspects of the product/system like function/component, system, performance, regression and service. Work with the development team to identify and capture test cases and ensure version management. Write security and stress tests. Setting up of test environments, designing test plans, developing test cases/scenarios/usage cases, and executing these cases. Providing feedback on usability and serviceability, trace the result to quality risk and report it to the concerned people. Testing the application programs as per testing plan. Preparing and tracking project-related Issue logs.</p>\r\n', 0, '2018-03-12 06:22:07', 'Permanent', '196085'),
