(12, 8, 'Full Stack Developer/lead - Node.js/ Angularjs', 'Software Developer/Designer', '17000', '20000', 'Experienced', '2', '5', 'Sector-63 Noida, India', 'Javascript, Node.Js, Angularjs, Html5, MongoDB, GIT, Server Side, Front End, HP Data Protector, Full Stack Developer, CSS3', '<p>Integration of user-facing elements developed by front-end developers with server-side logic<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Writing reusable, testable, and efficient code<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Design and implementation of low-latency, high-availability, and performant applications<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Implementation of security and data protection<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Integration of data storage solutions {{may include databases, key-value stores, blob stores, etc.}}<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Experience of Node.js and Angular js Mandatory.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- MongoDB preferable<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Basic understanding of front-end technologies, such as HTML5, and CSS3<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Understanding fundamental design principles behind a scalable application<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Proficient understanding of code versioning tools, such as Git</p>\r\n', 0, '2018-03-12 07:18:09', 'Permanent', '875916'),
