(15, 12, 'US IT Recruiter', 'Technical Recruiter', '', '', 'Experienced', '2', '4', 'Sector-63 Noida, India', 'The ideal candidate will be highly driven by superior communication and interpersonal skills.\r\n\r\nCandidate must be a quick learner with a positive attitude.\r\n\r\nShould have the ability to deliver results in fast paced & metrics driven environment.\r\n\r\nCandidate must be willing to work in permanent night shifts.', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Identify qualified candidates through various recruiting methods by using job boards (Dice, Monster, Career Builder etc.) &amp; networking websites (LinkedIn, indeed etc.)</li>\r\n	<li>Successfully match and qualify candidates based on their strengths vs. client requirements.</li>\r\n	<li>Conduct phone interviews, negotiate salary/hourly wage rates and other conditions of employment, gain acceptance from candidates on authorization to submit resume to clients, extend an offer of employment.</li>\r\n	<li>We are looking for stable resources that are looking for a long term opportunity.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 0, '2018-05-17 08:38:28', 'Permanent', '460319'),
(16, 11, 'IT Sales Manager', 'Sales / Business Development', '', '', 'Experienced', '3', '5', 'Sector-63 Noida, Uttar Pradesh, India', 'Team management and team building, reporting, work allocation, decision making skills as well as ability to make future strategies. Excellent communication skills, authoritative voice, email writing, basic business process knowledge, multilingual.', '<p>1. Minimum 3 years of experience in IT sales</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Have 2+ years of experience in bidding on various freelancing platforms, quality project selection and bidding on UpWork &amp; Guru etc. for mobile and web application development projects from overseas clients i.e. USA, UK, Australia &amp; Middle East.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Strong technical &amp; negotiation skills. Should be able to prepare estimates and proposals based on client requirements for web and mobile application development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Have experience in LinkedIn sales Navigator</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Able to coordinate with Lead generation team</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. Experience in Email Marketing and cold calling</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. Should be able to create different business proposal by own, send them to prospects, set the pricing model and close the leads.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. Must have 2-4 years of experience in Web Development &amp; Mobile Apps project acquisition &amp; closing&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9. Must have sound technical knowledge of advanced Web and Mobile technologies trending today&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10. Lead generation through Linkedin, database i.e. Zoominfo, Data.com and other social networks would be added value&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>11.Must be analytical enough to understand complex project requirements and prepare detailed proposal / bid to generate leads&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>12.Able to communicate with clients technically and prepare convincing write ups/messages&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>13. Expert in requirement gathering &amp; proposal / wire-frame drafting&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>14. Strong in logic / flow / technology and cost negotiation&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>15. Self motivated to meet sales target regularly&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;16. Proven new business development &#39;hunting&#39; experience with demonstrated consistency &nbsp;Have already closed Web &amp; Mobile Apps Development projects&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>17. Professional email, documents, presentation writing skills&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>18. Excellent verbal and written English skills for effective communication with overseas clients&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>19. American / British accent is MUST for efficient communication with International Clients. Hands-on experience and expertise in CLOSING the overseas leads / sales for Web and Mobile application development projects is MUST.</p>\r\n', 0, '2018-05-17 08:45:33', 'Permanent', '082439'),
(17, 11, 'Email Marketing Executive', 'Email Marketing', '', '', 'Experienced', '1', '2', 'Sector-63 Noida', 'The Email Marketing Specialist is responsible for managing and executing the production of email marketing campaigns, from planning through deployment and analysis. As part of the Digital Experience & Design team, they will focus on improving the overall inbox experience and collaborate with cross-functional teams in marketing, business, and creative to produce successful email marketing programs.', '<p>* Identify target audience and grow our email list/Data Mining</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Design and implement direct email marketing campaigns</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Proofread emails for clarity, grammar and spelling</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Write newsletters including all company updates</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Create email databases for lead generation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Analyze campaign performance and suggest improvements</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Ensure emails follow industry policies and best practices</p>\r\n', 0, '2018-05-19 04:50:17', 'Permanent', '512603');
